requests.name: Search Restaurants
requests.description:
##### Headers Parameters:
   
- Content-Type (application/json)
- Authorization (Bearer Auth_Key) (required if user looged in) | Obtained from login

##### Get Parameters:

##### Search Parameters:

- area (integer) (required)
- minimum_order_amount (string) (optinal) (range) (From,To) (1,20) 
- delivery_fee (string) (optinal) (range) (From,To) (1,500) 
- delivery_duration (integer) (optinal)
- ##### quick_filters Parameters (optinal):
- quick_filters=open,free_delivery,halal,accepts_vouchers,new_restaurant (optinal)
- ##### Sort Parameters (optinal):
- sort (optinal) (- For DESC) (* FOR ASC) (SORTING_FIELD)
- SORTING ONLY ON ONE FIELD
- SORTING_FIELD: res_status, favour_it, reviews_rank, name, minimum_order_amount, time_order_open, time_order_close, halal, featured, working_opening_hours, working_closing_hours,  delivery_fee, delivery_duration, accepts_vouchers
- DEFAULT_SORTING: res_status ASC, delivery_fee ASC ,delivery_duration ASC
- SORTING EX: sort=-res_status sort on res_status DESC
- SORTING EX: sort=*res_status sort on res_status ASC
- ##### Pagination Parameters (optinal):
- IF NO Pagination Parameters is set it will return all the records 
- ELSE IF Pagination Parameters is set:
- page (integer) (required)
- limit (integer) (required)
- ##### NOTE favour_it:
- IF Authorization is set it will return the favour_it restaurants of the client as 1
- IF Authorization not set it will return the favour_it as 0 for all the restaurants

##### Return:

- 200 Restaurant Objects or Empty Array
- 404 Not Found
- 405 Method Not Allowed
- 422 Validation Failed
